<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font style="" size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="">Hello&nbsp;</font><font style="">{!Contact.FirstName},</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font style="" size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">I tried calling you earlier but I was unable to reach you. I am attempting to contact you in regard to accessing our national tire accounts. Aside from fuel, tires are arguably the most sought after discount EDGE customers have available to them at no extra cost.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">As a Fleet One EDGE customer, one major benefit is access to our national account tire savings with&nbsp;<b>most major brands</b>, such as Goodyear, Michelin, Continental, Yokohama and more. Available nationwide, you'll pay the same low price whether you buy over-the-road or at your local dealer. Billing is available right through your Fleet One EDGE card (<i>other payment options also available</i>).&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Current customers are already saving an average of&nbsp;<b>$50 per tire</b>. Learn more and request a quote at&nbsp;<a href="http://fleetoneedge.com/gold">fleetoneedge.com/gold</a>.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif" style="">If you decide you would like to utilize our tire pricing, give me a call and I will send you out a price sheet that includes the type of tire(s) you are looking for. You can also just email me back the brand, size, type of tire and I will send you over customized tire pricing.</font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Thank you,</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;{!User.LastName}</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">EDGE Benefits</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Phone:&nbsp;</font>{!User.Phone}</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Email:&nbsp;</font>{!User.Email}</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font style="" size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Website: www.fleetoneedge.com</span>&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
